outputs.output_descr: Reducing the incidence of Brucellosis in animal and humans through yearly mass vaccination campaigns and building the public and private institutional, human and physical capacities to control the disease

Reducing the incidence of Brucellosis in animal and humans through yearly mass vaccination campaigns and building the public and private institutional, human and physical capacities to control the disease

project_descr: The project was to contribute to a measurable reduction of the causes and incidence of Brucellosis in small ruminants, predominantly, sheep and goats, as well as humans in the PTs.
